{"tid":746005,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【再涉抄襲日動漫】《我不是藥神》急刪慶祝海報 「真誠致歉」","createTime":"2018-07-17T08:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T10:43:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"570f6e88ef9839b01e29edfe13e3a87eb6d02576","tid":746005,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180717/large/1531801525_da5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180717%2Flarge%2F1531801525_da5a.jpg&h=247c5824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180717/large/1531801526_4c3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180717%2Flarge%2F1531801526_4c3b.jpg&h=1868479a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180717/large/1531801529_9794.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180717%2Flarge%2F1531801529_9794.jpg&h=42148945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由真人真事改編的內地電影《我不是藥神》，講述主角為救患血癌父親，從印度引入仿製抗癌藥，之後再為其他病友代購藥物。該電影被認為是反映中國「不敢病，病不起」的悲涼現實，大受歡迎，官方周一為收得25億人民幣（下同，約29億港元）票房發佈慶祝海報，卻被眼尖網民發現，海報涉嫌抄襲日本動漫。<br />\n<br />\n有網民指出，《我不是藥神》慶祝電影達25億票房的海報，涉嫌抄襲日本動漫《我的英雄學院》。海報可見，《我不是藥神》的人物姿勢、在海報上的擺放位置，都跟後者十分相似。此外，電影早前的慶祝海報亦被指抄襲《海賊王》。<br />\n<br />\n《我不是藥神》官方發現事件後，發聲明認錯，聲明中寫道「海報整體設計與日本動漫《我的英雄學院》海報雷同，涉嫌侵權。作為電影新媒體海報製作方，正經圖畫在此向廣大網友真誠致歉。創意是海報的靈魂，每一份創意都值得尊重，由於我們製作上的不嚴謹，給喜歡電影的廣大影迷以及動漫迷們造成了傷害，我們深表歉意。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180717/58451766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F58451766&d=dY1SNdcIbrVQgb7bjg36EcKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=75e0abe0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180717%2F58451766&h=36297884\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180717/58451766</a>"},{"pid":"4c093e88dbb9bcf244189f1fce7d7c1de823e6e9","tid":746005,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:34:18.000Z","msg":"連改下d位都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04310afdc9d5de054922e46ab74bfafd8aba68b3","tid":746005,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"準確啲講, 應該叫臨摹?"},{"pid":"7153a2c428c4252e215995006cd7bacdc9f9c099","tid":746005,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:34:59.000Z","msg":"竟然有道歉"},{"pid":"c5800426fabf96c8c3f3eb4dd03ba9501b560c9f","tid":746005,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7153a2c428c4252e215995006cd7bacdc9f9c099","tid":746005,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:34:59.000Z","msg":"竟然有道歉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"後台唔夠人勁仲唔道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6476d11ecf5fa695e419e288af8f6deaf3873e","tid":746005,"uid":95452,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"04310afdc9d5de054922e46ab74bfafd8aba68b3","tid":746005,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"準確啲講, 應該叫臨摹?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:37:47.000Z","msg":"準確啲講，應該係日本仔坐時光機抄佢啲海報"},{"pid":"d1911cec02ba86f1b364b15a6ec87ba64e7d4e14","tid":746005,"uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5800426fabf96c8c3f3eb4dd03ba9501b560c9f","tid":746005,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7153a2c428c4252e215995006cd7bacdc9f9c099","tid":746005,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17